    {
        "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778094",
        "quote": "At thirteen, I accompanied my mother to the Hawaiian Islands. There, for the first time, I saw the wonder of a steamship and the vastness of the ocean. From that time on, I was eager to acquire the knowledge of the West and to fathom the mysteries of nature.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Sun Yat-sen",
            "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778094"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
