                "name": "Country",
                "url": "/topics/country"
            },
            {
                "name": "Develop",
                "url": "/topics/develop"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778132",
        "quote": "We are the poorest and weakest state in the world, occupying the lowest position in international affairs; the rest of mankind is the carving knife and the serving dish, while we are the fish and the meat.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Sun Yat-sen",
            "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778132"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Rest",
                "url": "/topics/rest"
            },
            {
                "name": "Mankind",
                "url": "/topics/mankind"
            },
            {
                "name": "Occupying",
                "url": "/topics/occupying"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778126",
        "quote": "Because of poverty, we must adopt the capitalist means of production to develop our resources to get rich. However, if we ignore the issue of social justice at the beginning of China's industrialization, we will sow the seeds of class warfare in the future.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Sun Yat-sen",
            "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778126"
        },
