                "url": "/topics/however"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778146",
        "quote": "The government should help and guide the weak and small racial groups within its national boundaries toward self-determination and self-government. It should offer resistance to foreign aggression, and simultaneously, it should revise foreign treaties in order to restore our equality and independence among the nations.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Sun Yat-sen",
            "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778146"
        },
