                "url": "/topics/treaties"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778095",
        "quote": "The goal of the revolution is to achieve the people's rights, but during the course of the revolution, we must stress military power - and the two are mutually contradictory.",
