                "url": "/topics/thousand_years"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778147",
        "quote": "We know a way now to make use of democracy, and we know how to change the attitude of people towards government, but yet the majority of people are without vision. We who have prevision must lead them and guide them into the right way if we want to escape the confusions of Western democracy and not follow in the tracks of the West.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Sun Yat-sen",
            "url": "/quotes/sun_yatsen_778147"
        },
